verses.roman:
tāṅra śiṣya--govinda pūjaka caitanya-dāsa
mukundānanda cakravartī, premī kṛṣṇadāsa

synonyms: tāṅra śiṣya—his disciple; govinda—the Govinda Deity; pūjaka—priest; caitanya-dāsa—of the name Caitanya dāsa; mukundānanda cakravartī—of the name Mukundānanda Cakravartī; premī—a great lover; kṛṣṇadāsa—of the name Kṛṣṇadāsa.
translation: Among his disciples were Caitanya dāsa, who was a priest of the Govinda Deity, as well as Mukundānanda Cakravartī and the great devotee Kṛṣṇadāsa.
